Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: telegram-spotted-dmi-bot
Version: 3.1.0
Summary: Telegram-SpottedDMI-Bot is the platform that powers @Spotted_DMI_Bot, a Telegram bot that let students send an anonymous message to the channel community
Author: drendog, Helias, Herbrant, alepiaz, TaToTanWeb, FilippoMarletta
Author-email: TendTo <casablancaerneto@gmail.com>
